Class 10

How to handle Calendars:
1.Click on the calendar
2.Locate the month and get text
3.if the desired text is not visible ---> we will keep clicking on next
4. as soon as we have the desired month ---> then grab all the cells/ dates from  the table
5. store them in a list and loop through them
6. if condition to match cell value with condition ----> then click on the matched date and break loop


Why do we need screenshots in testing?
in testing it is very important to take screenshots in order to prove that our  test scenario
covered certain functionality

In selenium in order to take screenshots we will be using TakesScreenShots interface


Actions Class
    Actions Class is given by selenium to capture keyboard and mouse events such as:

    Move to element
    drag and drop
    double click
    right click

